                "invention-title": [
                    "Water-soluble condensed carbon nitride as well as preparation method and application thereof",
                    "一种水溶性凝聚态氮化碳及其制备方法与应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention provides water-soluble condensed-state carbon nitride as well as a preparation method and application thereof, and the method comprises the following steps: carrying out solid-liquid phase thermal polymerization reaction on a carbon nitride precursor under the condition of a cyano anion-containing molten salt system to prepare the water-soluble condensed-state carbon nitride with high yield. According to the invention, the problems of low light radiation excitation efficiency of a bulk phase structure and low yield caused by difficult polymerization due to poor water solubility and a thick block structure of traditional carbon nitride are solved. The prepared water-soluble condensed-state carbon nitride has penetrable surface-phase penetrating radiation and strong capturing and adsorbing capacity on water molecules, so that more photo-generated charges can be excited to the greatest extent, and redox reaction of water can be quickly carried out; the method is expected to be applied to large-scale photocatalytic decomposition of water to produce hydrogen, carbon dioxide reduction, nitrogen fixation, organic synthesis and other reactions."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供一种水溶性凝聚态氮化碳及其制备方法与应用，方法包括步骤：将氮化碳前驱体在含氰基阴离子的熔盐体系条件下进行固‑液相的热聚合反应，高产率制得了水溶性凝聚态氮化碳。本发明解决了传统氮化碳因水溶性差和厚块体结构导致其体相结构光辐射激发效率低以及聚合困难导致低产的问题。由于制备所得的水溶性凝聚态氮化碳具有穿透性的表‑相贯穿辐射和对水分子的强捕获吸附能力，可最大程度地激发产生更多的光生电荷，并迅速发生水的氧化还原反应，有望应用于大规模光催化分解水产氢、二氧化碳还原、氮气固定以及有机合成等反应。"
                }
            ]
